data.description: Ranch home situated among the newer homes in the Riverview Court subdivision, a pleasing cul-de-sac setting of newer homes, located near the Belle River, Professionally constructed in 2022, of 2 x 6 construction, boasting of an open floor plan featuring white cabinetry, grey granite countertops, large island, breakfast nook, cathedral ceilings, GE stainless steel appliances purchased in 2022, and wood laminate planking floors, which extend into the primary suite, with walk-in closet, ceramic bath, double sinks and shower.  First floor laundry is at the garage entry with plenty of closet space.. A vinyl and stone veneer front leads calls you inside.. the back yard features a six foot privacy fence, and patio.  Assumable mortgage at well below current mortgage rates to qualified buyers.
